text:
Khloe Kardashian has fired back at haters who criticised her workout regime.

The reality star, who is already six months gone, took part in a gruelling home workout alongside her sister Kourtney earlier this week.

However, Khloe's regime was soon met with criticism from some fans, though the KUWTK beauty didn't waste any time before putting them in their place.

(Image: Snapchat) (Image: Snapchat)

She tweeted a link to an article stating 33 reasons why it is beneficial to work out while pregnant.

Khloe added: For the ones who think they are physicians all of a sudden but MY doctor and I communicate and my workouts are cleared and highly recommended.

"Thanks kiddos! Don't make me stop sharing s**t."

The video shared on social media showed 33-year-old Khloe flaunting her growing baby bump as she worked out in a pair of leggings and a black hoody.

(Image: Snapchat)

At the end of the workout, Khloe told her fans: "Kourtney and I did a lot of other s**t that we didn't snap because it just wasn't cute.

"We did abs and what else? Leg work and floor exercises where it's not the best angle."

(Image: Snapchat) (Image: Snapchat)

Video Loading Video Unavailable Click to play Tap to play The video will start in 8 Cancel Play now

Her clap back comes after she revealed she was six months pregnant as she attended the star-studded Kardashian Christmas party in a stunning embellished jumpsuit.

It was the first time pregnant Khloe has been seen in public since she announced she was expecting her first baby with boyfriend Tristan Thompson after months of rumours.

In an Instagram post, Khloe said: "Merry Christmas!! May you sparkle and shine this festive season, may all of your wishes and dreams come true.

"I pray that we all may feel this happiness all year round. God bless you! #BabyBump"

(Image: khloekardashian/Instagram)

(Image: Snapchat/Khloe Kardashian) (Image: Snapchat/Khloe Kardashian)

Khloe also revealed how far along she is, telling a fan on social media: "I'll be 6 months next week".

Posing with elder sister Kim, who is expecting her third child via surrogate, on Snapchat earlier on Christmas Eve, Khloe was dressed to impress in a festive gold dress as she rang in the holidays with her famous family.

"I know what you all really want to see," Kim teased her followers before moving the camera down to give a flash of her Khloe's tum.

Only too happy to oblige, proud mum-to-be Khloe then gently caressed her tiny bump over her sparkly gown.
title: Pregnant Khloe Kardashian fires back at haters who criticise her workout regime - 'They're cleared and highly recommended!'
